body: We tried implementing per-row quantization and found it introduces performance regression, so we didn't merge it into 1.7.
@yufenglee is batch inference supported in onnxruntime?
@isgursoy and @rohanshingade, we tried per-row quantization but were not able to get better performance. We will not support per-row quantization.
